data.description: An exceptional opportunity to acquire an updated residence priced $250,000. Live within your own four walls in this charming bungalow.  Clean and thoughtful updates, including newer appliances, an air conditioning system, and new flooring. Tucked away from the main road, it provides a peaceful retreat while remaining conveniently situated. Beyond the aesthetic appeal, this home represents a prudent investment, making homeownership an attainable reality. Schedule a viewing today to fully appreciate the unique benefits this home brings to the market. All facts and figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only, Buyer is to verify all.
